sources.title: Sounds of the 70's : My Sharona
sources.description:
Travel back in time with the sounds of the 1970's, and tune in to the beat of Hot Chocolate, Smokey, Pilot, The Stranglers, Dr Feelgood, Talking Heads, Real Thing, The Knack, Lynyrd Skinyrd, Steve Harley & Cockney Rebel, 10cc, Marshall Hain

Every programme includes newsreel from the time, with facts and information about the artists and the songs. Unforgettable sounds and stories of the 70's


Director: Jason Fenwick
Year 2021
